metadata.name: Babyccino #1
metadata.description: Fueled by caffeine, milk, and sugar, these #tinybuymighty Babyccinos are on a mission to save the world from bad coffee and anyone trying to steal the powers of this precious bean. Stored on the Ethereum Blockchain, each Babyccino NFT has an ambitious baby attached to a coffee/espresso based beverage celebrating the imagination, curiosity, and mischievousness of being a kid while also being a little boujee about coffee. These Babyccinos will teach you a little more about coffee and encourage your creativity while battling any bad brew that comes your way! 15% goes to supporting kids who cant read good & want to learn how to do other stuff good too
